<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p><rs type="material">White marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">statue base</rs> with moulded <rs type="objectType">panel</rs>s on three sides (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.55</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">1.11</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.54</measure>) broken below and at the upper left corner of the front face, which is also worn.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> (a) on the front face, (b) on the right side. The moulding is complete above; the text must have begun on a crowning feature.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Second to third centuries A.D.; <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.025</measure>; very similar to those of <xref type="iAph">1045</xref> (=MAMA 524); apices on the numerals in b. 3.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notAfter="0300" notBefore="0212" exact="none">Third century A.D.</date>
(<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>, <rs type="criteria">nomenclature</rs>)</p>
</div>
